            "id": 5901359,
            "title": "台股安啦有大人哥在照顧、廣宇+20%廣宇第二今日進場",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股安啦！有大人哥在照顧<br/>\n雖然在利空未除之前，短線震盪難免，不過，從散裝航運慧洋 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2637:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2637\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2637-TW</a>)、裕民 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2606:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2606\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2606-TW</a>)、台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>)、台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)、大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>)… 等受惠烏俄重建商機加持，今日持續展現強勢上攻的企圖心；再到記憶體品安 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8088:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8088\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8088-TW</a>)、威剛 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>)、電子通路亞矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6113:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6113\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6113-TW</a>)、茂綸 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6227:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6227\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6227-TW</a>)、安馳 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3528:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3528\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3528-TW</a>)、電源供應器盛達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3027-TW</a>)、軍工保勝光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6517:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6517\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6517-TW</a>)… 等低基期轉機股接續強勢大漲上來，以及矽光子上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>)、波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>)、電源管理 IC 矽力 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6415:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6415\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6415-TW</a>)、AI 伺服器概念股 jpp-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5284:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5284\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5284-TW</a>)、面板群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、設備信紘科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6667:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6667\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6667-TW</a>)、資訊服務凌群 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2453:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2453\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2453-TW</a>)、機器人所羅門 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2359:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2359\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2359-TW</a>)… 等接續回穩大漲上來顯見市場聰明的資金開始逢低默默撿便宜，不曉得你有沒有發覺到？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>加上英特爾拚轉股，新任 CEO 陳立武透露，公司旗下設計和 IFS(晶圓代工服務)二大部門預計維持現況，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 鬆口氣；AI 伺服器龍頭鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 利空洗盤雙腳築底，醞釀絕佳好機會，以及年線持續震盪走揚向上不變，年線代表著長期的趨勢及方向，年線未下彎之前，就不能說長期趨勢已走空；因此，若無意外的話，預期快則下周 3/17 日輝達 GTC 大會前後、慢則待 4/2 日對等關稅議題明朗化後，一波絕地大反攻的行情隨時將可望孕育而生，這是大家可留意與掌握的機會。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>廣宇 + 20% 廣宇第二今日進場<br/>\n鴻海集團旗下線材廠【廣宇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2328-TW</a>)】<br/>\n跨足 AI 與機器人領域有成<br/>\n加上富爸爸鴻海集團的加持、營運現轉機<br/>\n3/6 日 46.5 元低接全力鎖定之後<br/>\n大師兄也都無私與大家一同分享<br/>\n短短 6 個交易日現賺 + 20%<br/>\n相信你們都看到了<br/>\n一切都敢講在前面<br/>\n感謝大家共襄盛舉</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>廣宇第二【6 開頭低基期轉機成長股】<br/>\n搭上機器人暨自動化概念商機題材<br/>\n去年 Q4 轉虧為盈、每股賺 0.87 元<br/>\n2 月營收月增逾 50%、年增逾 206%，累計前 2 月營收年增逾 157%<br/>\n營運處在於成長的浪頭上<br/>\n低檔量增、雙腳築底、慣性改變<br/>\n一切才剛剛開始<br/>\n歡迎大家一起共襄盛舉<br/>\n想要跟上的好朋友<br/>\n歡迎加 Line 私訊大師兄… 留言〝+1〞<br/>\n留下你的姓名及連絡電話<br/>\n大師兄手把手帶你來佈局<br/>\n你不足的信心<br/>\n團隊用實戰績效來幫你堆積<br/>\n讓你先賺再說<br/>\n聯鈞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3450:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3450\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3450-TW</a>)、亞光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3019:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3019\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3019-TW</a>) 及和椿 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6215:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6215\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6215-TW</a>) 財富翻倍<br/>\n相信你們也都看到了<br/>\n想賺大的、就趁現在</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><div class=\"youtube-embed-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;padding-top:30px;height:0;overflow:hidden;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/5UJpbNycIQU\" style=\"position: absolute;top: 0;left: 0;width: 100%;height: 100%;\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>工商時報績效競賽 13 冠王、卓越績效傲視同業、專業實力有目共賭！<br/>\n更多第一手訊息、以及飆股機會→請加入大師兄飆股鑫天地的大家族<br/>\nLINE@連結網址：<a href=\"https://line.me/R/ti/p/@gold99\">https://line.me/R/ti/p/%40gold99</a><br/>\nTelegram 連結網址：<a href=\"https://t.me/gold0999\">https://t.me/gold0999</a><br/>\n諮詢專線︰02-23219933(24 小時專人服務)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"308\" data-mime=\"image/png\" data-ratio=\"1.698051948051948\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5901359/m/11c9c8bca779f1855ce799bbaf54d01b.jpg\" data-width=\"523\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5901359/l/11c9c8bca779f1855ce799bbaf54d01b.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>文章來源：倫元投顧陳學進分析師</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\">本公司所推薦分析之個別有價證券無不當之財務利益關係以往之績效不保證未來獲利投資人應獨立判斷審慎評估並自負投資風險</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
